---
title: FundaConnect — Booking Flow
---
flowchart TD
    A[Parent browses teachers] --> B[Selects teacher + subject + slot]
    B --> C{Slot available?}
    C -->|No| D[Show alternative slots]
    D --> B
    C -->|Yes| E[Lock slot in Redis - 15min TTL]
    E --> F[Create booking - pending_payment]
    F --> G[Generate PayFast payment URL]
    G --> H[Redirect parent to PayFast]
    H --> I{Payment outcome}
    I -->|Success ITN| J[Validate ITN signature]
    J --> K[Booking → confirmed]
    K --> L[Generate meeting link]
    L --> M[Send confirmation SMS + email]
    I -->|Cancelled| N[Release slot lock]
    N --> O[Booking → cancelled]
    I -->|Timeout 15min| P[Release slot lock]
    P --> Q[Booking → expired]

    M --> R[Lesson takes place]
    R --> S[Teacher marks complete]
    S --> T[Booking → completed]
    T --> U[Prompt parent for review]
    T --> V[Queue teacher payout]

---
title: FundaConnect — Teacher Verification
---
flowchart TD
    A[Teacher registers] --> B[verification_status = pending]
    B --> C[Upload required documents]
    C --> D{All 5 docs uploaded?}
    D -->|No| C
    D -->|Yes| E[verification_status = documents_submitted]
    E --> F[Admin notification: new verification]
    F --> G[Admin reviews documents]
    G --> H{All approved?}
    H -->|Yes| I[verification_status = verified]
    I --> J[Profile visible in search]
    I --> K[Confirmation email to teacher]
    H -->|No| L[verification_status = rejected]
    L --> M[Rejection email with reasons]
    M --> N[Teacher corrects & re-uploads]
    N --> E

---
title: FundaConnect — Payment & Payout Flow
---
flowchart TD
    A[Parent books lesson - R250] --> B[PayFast processes payment]
    B --> C[Funds held in platform account]
    C --> D[Lesson delivered]
    D --> E[Teacher marks complete]
    E --> F[Calculate commission - 17.5%]
    F --> G[Platform fee: R43.75]
    F --> H[Teacher share: R206.25]
    H --> I[Queue for weekly payout]
    I --> J{Monday 06:00 SAST}
    J --> K[Batch process payouts]
    K --> L[Transfer to teacher bank account]
    L --> M[Payout confirmation email]
